            "text": "Datadog query: @run_id:r-9281 @event:tool_start. Timeline shows search 800ms, then delete_file ERROR permission_denied. Engineer fixes role mapping — no LLM change needed. Alert fires on rate(@event:tool_failed[5m]) > 50."
